    • Method Detail

      • onApplied

        void onApplied(LocationParametersUpdate update)
        Callback method that indicates that the LocationParametersUpdate has been successfully applied.
        Parameters:
        update - object that contains the new parameters applied to the location system.

      • onError

        void onError(Error error)
        The LocationParametersUpdate could not be applied because of an error. Either it's an invalid update (parameters are not correct) or incompatible with actual parameters of the location system. To see more details of what's happening you can check the error details
        Parameters:
        error - object that contains additional information on why the update failed.
